✗ "Verb Substitution", "Word Substitution", "Noun Deletion" — grammatical class is too vague; use the acoustic or linguistic cause you identified in your reasoning instead.
Do not combine multiple error types with "&", "/", "+", or "and" — pick the one that had the most impact on meaning.
* If no meaningful word-level error exists (e.g., only punctuation differs), leave all final_answer fields empty.

